"stockwatch","ARG","Amerigo Resources Ltd","2026-02-25","NEWS_RELEASE_EN","not applicable","NewsRelease","Amerigo Announces Strong 2025 Results & Quarterly Dividend","https://www.stockwatch.com/News/Item/Z-C!ARG-3788901/C/ARG","3788901","https://www.stockwatch.com/News/Sedardoc/6131896.pdf","","0","0","no","","2026-02-25 07:30 ET - News Release
