"stockwatch","ARG","Amerigo Resources Ltd","2025-10-29","NEWS_RELEASE_EN","not applicable","NewsRelease","Amerigo Announces Q3-2025 Results, Full Debt Repayment and Quarterly Dividend Increase","https://www.stockwatch.com/News/Item/Z-C!ARG-3746314/C/ARG","3746314","https://www.stockwatch.com/News/Sedardoc/6042248.pdf","","0","0","no","","2025-10-29 07:30 ET - News Release
